
"smart_sources:Research/@wong_relationships_2020.md": {"path":"Research/@wong_relationships_2020.md","last_embed":{"hash":null},"embeddings":{},"last_read":{"hash":"rnef6d","at":1774951884833},"class_name":"SmartSource","last_import":{"mtime":1774951829817,"size":3467,"at":1774951884834,"hash":"rnef6d"},"blocks":{"#---frontmatter---":[1,96],"#Relationships between Mitochondrial Dysfunction and Neurotransmission Failure in Alzheimer’s Disease":[98,102],"#Relationships between Mitochondrial Dysfunction and Neurotransmission Failure in Alzheimer’s Disease#{1}":[100,102]},"outlinks":[{"title":"Author/Kan Yin Wong","target":"Author/Kan Yin Wong","line":75},{"title":"Author/K. Y. Wong","target":"Author/K. Y. Wong","line":76},{"title":"Author/Jaydeep Roy","target":"Author/Jaydeep Roy","line":77},{"title":"Author/J. Roy","target":"Author/J. Roy","line":78},{"title":"Author/Jaydeep Roy","target":"Author/Jaydeep Roy","line":79},{"title":"Author/Man Lung Fung","target":"Author/Man Lung Fung","line":80},{"title":"Author/M. L. Fung","target":"Author/M. L. Fung","line":81},{"title":"Author/Man-Lung Fung","target":"Author/Man-Lung Fung","line":82},{"title":"Author/Boon Chin Heng","target":"Author/Boon Chin Heng","line":83},{"title":"Author/Boon Chin Heng","target":"Author/Boon Chin Heng","line":84},{"title":"Author/Bca Heng","target":"Author/Bca Heng","line":85},{"title":"Author/Boon Chin Heng","target":"Author/Boon Chin Heng","line":86},{"title":"Author/Boon Chin Heng","target":"Author/Boon Chin Heng","line":87},{"title":"Author/Chengfei Zhang","target":"Author/Chengfei Zhang","line":88},{"title":"Author/C. Zhang","target":"Author/C. Zhang","line":89},{"title":"Author/Chengfei Zhang","target":"Author/Chengfei Zhang","line":90},{"title":"Author/Lee Wei Lim","target":"Author/Lee Wei Lim","line":91},{"title":"Author/Lee Wei Lim","target":"Author/Lee Wei Lim","line":92}],"metadata":{"id":"wong_relationships_2020","type":"article-journal","title":"Relationships between Mitochondrial Dysfunction and Neurotransmission Failure in Alzheimer’s Disease","issued":{"date-parts":[[2020]]},"DOI":"null","container-title":"null","abstract":"Besides extracellular deposition of amyloid beta and formation of phosphorylated tau in the brains of patients with Alzheimer's disease (AD), the pathogenesis of AD is also thought to involve mitochondrial dysfunctions and altered neurotransmission systems. However, none of these components can describe the diverse cognitive, behavioural, and psychiatric symptoms of AD without the pathologies interacting with one another. The purpose of this review is to understand the relationships between mitochondrial and neurotransmission dysfunctions in terms of (1) how mitochondrial alterations affect cholinergic and monoaminergic systems via disruption of energy metabolism, oxidative stress, and apoptosis; and (2) how different neurotransmission systems drive mitochondrial dysfunction via increasing amyloid beta internalisation, oxidative stress, disruption of mitochondrial permeabilisation, and mitochondrial trafficking. All these interactions are separately discussed in terms of neurotransmission systems. The association of mitochondrial dysfunctions with alterations in dopamine, norepinephrine, and histamine is the prospective goal in this research field. By unfolding the complex interactions surrounding mitochondrial dysfunction in AD, we can better develop potential treatments to delay, prevent, or cure this devastating disease.","tags":["#literature_note"],"author":[{"family":"Wong","given":"Kan Yin","literal":""},{"family":"Wong","given":"K. Y.","literal":""},{"family":"Roy","given":"Jaydeep","literal":""},{"family":"Roy","given":"J.","literal":""},{"family":"Roy","given":"Jaydeep","literal":""},{"family":"Fung","given":"Man Lung","literal":""},{"family":"Fung","given":"M. L.","literal":""},{"family":"Fung","given":"Man-Lung","literal":""},{"family":"Heng","given":"Boon Chin","literal":""},{"family":"Heng","given":"Boon Chin","literal":""},{"family":"Heng","given":"Bca","literal":""},{"family":"Heng","given":"Boon Chin","literal":""},{"family":"Heng","given":"Boon Chin","literal":""},{"family":"Zhang","given":"Chengfei","literal":""},{"family":"Zhang","given":"C.","literal":""},{"family":"Zhang","given":"Chengfei","literal":""},{"family":"Lim","given":"Lee Wei","literal":""},{"family":"Lim","given":"Lee Wei","literal":""}],"citation-key":"wong_relationships_2020","year":"2020","dateCreated":"2026-03-31","reading-status":"to-read","aliases":["Relationships between Mitochondrial Dysfunction and Neurotransmission Failure in Alzheimer’s Disease"],"author-links":["[[Author/Kan Yin Wong]]","[[Author/K. Y. Wong]]","[[Author/Jaydeep Roy]]","[[Author/J. Roy]]","[[Author/Jaydeep Roy]]","[[Author/Man Lung Fung]]","[[Author/M. L. Fung]]","[[Author/Man-Lung Fung]]","[[Author/Boon Chin Heng]]","[[Author/Boon Chin Heng]]","[[Author/Bca Heng]]","[[Author/Boon Chin Heng]]","[[Author/Boon Chin Heng]]","[[Author/Chengfei Zhang]]","[[Author/C. Zhang]]","[[Author/Chengfei Zhang]]","[[Author/Lee Wei Lim]]","[[Author/Lee Wei Lim]]"],"attachment":[],"related":[[]]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[]},
